353リムサ・ロミンサ演説部屋
385First Dicasterial Observatorium of Aetherial and Astrological Phenomena
529Ser Aucheforne of the High Tide's Cell
2325The Supreme Sacred Tribunal of Halonic Inquisitory Doctrine
2824The Bridge of the High Rule Warriors
2989Leaving naught in their wake but blood and ash.
2990Thus did the first doom befall us.
2992For soon did the sun bend low
2993Thus did the second doom break us.
2994Yet it was neither claw nor flame
2995Stacked to the heavens where they took root
2996Thus did the third doom undo us.
